\intbl \ql \b Background\b0 \line The University of Mangosuthu is a public higher education institution and has programmes that are accredited by the Council on Higher Education \'28CHE\'29. \line \line The Institution is applying for the accreditation of an Advanced Diploma in Accounting programme to be offered in the contact Mode and at its main campus. \line \line The Institution is accredited to offer an Advanced Diploma in Cost \'26 Management Accounting programme.\line \line The University submitted the following Cost and Management Accounting programmes during the HEQSF-alignment process\'3A \line - Diploma in Cost and Management Accounting \'28HEQSF-aligned\'29 \line - Bachelor of Technology\'3A Cost and Management Accounting \'28Non-HEQSF-aligned\'2C Category C programme\'29\cell \pard 

